snippet.title: The Collar: Update 1 (Trailer)
snippet.description:
Website: https://arizonainkstudios.com/the-collar

The first of many updates to The Collar. It has been 1 year since the release and this is a full update of new maps, new mechanics, faster gameplay, bug fixes, performance enhancements, and much, much more!

Only one will survive.
Kill or be killed. Your choice.
The Collar doesn't care.

#thecollar #collargame #thecollargame
